  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "09bb2a41-666e-4287-adfe-a8f268d5e802",
    "name": "SSLCommerz Payment Gateway API",
    "description": "Complete SSLCommerz payment gateway integration with sandbox testing\n\n### A. Correct Payment Flow\n\n1. Initialize Payment Session  \n    (You already did this. You get sessionkey, tran_id, and GatewayPageURL.)\n    \n2. Redirect the User to GatewayPageURL  \n    \\- The user must complete the payment on the SSLCommerz page.\n    \n3. After Payment Completion  \n    \\- SSLCommerz will call your success_url, fail_url, or cancel_url (as provided in your request).  \n    \\- You will receive a val_id or sessionkey in the callback.\n    \n4. Validate the Payment  \n    \\- Now, use the val_id or sessionkey you received in the callback to validate the payment.  \n    \\- Only after the payment is completed will the validation endpoint return a valid transaction.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "22880749"
  },
